### Smart Image Analyzer - Lab 2 Test Requests
### These tests are for the HTTP results endpoint.
### Image uploads must be done via Azure Storage Explorer or curl (see README).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071

### Test 1: Get all analysis results (default limit: 10)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results

### Test 2: Get all results with custom limit
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results?limit=5

### Test 3: Get a specific result by ID
### After running Test 1, copy an "id" from the response and paste it below
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results/4e26c5a1-7a20-4176-8d5c-03e5dfaaddda

### Test 4: Get results with limit of 1 (most recent only)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results?limit=1

### Test 5: Try to get a non-existent result (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results/does-not-exist-id